It’s MY BIRTHDAY 🥳 ❤️💕💜🎉
Ahhh wow God, you ARE so GOOD!!

For a moment, today I stop to reflect on my life. The impact that I have had on the world. The gifts, hugs, laughter, smiles, tears, growth and LOVE I have been able to endure and cherish. 

Today, I stop to give myself flowers not just for the occasion but simply because i’ve earned them. I am grateful to have another chance at life. Here’s to year ✨25✨🥳💕🎉🎉🎉

I just wanted to take a moment and say "thank you" to everyone for all of the birthday wishes. It means a lot to me that you all took time from your busy lives to wish me a happy birthday. 

I am truly touched by the sheer number of messages and phone calls I received for my birthday. I genuinely enjoyed reading all of your lovely comments, they each touched my heart. Thank to my friends and family for gifts and love. I AM GRATEFUL 🥹 🥳💜🤗
